n":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2794684453","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2794684453","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjc5NDY4NDQ1Mw==","status":"current","title":"Guía de Proyectos","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":44304407},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2794684453/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2794684453/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2794684453/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2794684453/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2794684453","tinyui":"/x/JYCTpg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2794684453","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2794684453/Gu+a+de+Proyectos","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2794684453"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"8a2c300c-df10-4d3d-9387-abdc47965457\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Bancard cuenta con m&uacute;ltiples servicios que proveen soluciones para los distintos modelos de negocio que maneja.</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"1f5b07ef-9cf3-4ebd-a03f-5d1c1bde8f74\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 207.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 300.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 253.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Servicio</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Funcionalidad</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Repositorio</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Audit-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Cada acci&oacute;n que se realiza en os portales se registra en audit como un log. Ej: &ldquo;El usuario XX intent&oacute; loguearse al portal de comercios&rdquo; </p></li><li><p>Servicio responsable de mantener y servir informaci&oacute;n de auditor&iacute;a</p></li><li><p>Acciones de usuario</p></li><li><p>Llamadas a API</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-audit-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-audit-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p><ac:link><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Auth Service\" ri:version-at-save=\"4\" /><ac:link-body>Auth-service</ac:link-body></ac:link></p></td><td><ul><li><p>Manejo de usuarios</p></li><li><p>Manejo de autenticaci&oacute;n de servicios y portales</p></li><li><p>Base de datos MySQL (auth_service_production)</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-auth-service\"><u>https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-auth-service</u></a></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Backend-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicio que da soporte al Backend administrativo de bancard</p></li><li><p>Proxy entre servicios y backend administrativo</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-backend-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-backend-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Billing-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Consultar facturas</p></li><li><p>Pagar una factura</p></li><li><p>Especificaci&oacute;n de los productos (ej: Recarga de minutos)</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-billing-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-billing-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Biller-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Para que Billing-service pueda consultar facturas y pagar. Los facturadores deben implementar una API.</p></li><li><p>Biller implementa esta api para facturadores chicos y acepta la informaci&oacute;n de las facturas a trav&eacute;s de un CSV</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-biller-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-biller-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Billing-service-public-proxy</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Interfaz p&uacute;blica de Billing para que entidades puedan utilizar en su home banking:</p><ul><li><p>Consulta de Facturas</p></li><li><p>Pago de Facturas</p></li></ul></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-billing-service-public-proxy\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-billing-service-public-proxy</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Commerce-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Manejo de comercios-entidades</p></li><li><p>Se reciben transacciones desde el BUS y a partir de estas se crean los comercios, tipos de tarjetas</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-commerce-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-commerce-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>ePOS-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicio que da soporte a boca web</p></li><li><p>Servicio de pago de facturas para bocas (Redes de cobranza como Abitad - RedPagos en Uruguay)</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-epos-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-epos-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Loyalty-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicio para hacer campa&ntilde;as de lealtad</p></li><li><p>Principalmente para entidades</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-loyalty-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-loyalty-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>mPOS-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicio que da soporte a la aplicaci&oacute;n m&oacute;vil MiniPOS</p></li><li><p>Les permite a los comercios utilizar smartphone como un POS en cualquier lugar</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-mpos-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-mpos-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Notifications-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Encargado de almacenar todas las transacciones de las tarjetas de cr&eacute;dito y d&eacute;bito</p></li><li><p>Encargado de enviar notificaciones push</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-notification-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-notification-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Payment-link-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Allows commerces to create new payments without the need of hardware like cardscanners. </p></li><li><p>The commerces will be able to generate payment links that can be shared to customers so they can make a payment only by opening the link.</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-payment-link-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-payment-link-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p><ac:link><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Auth Service\" ri:version-at-save=\"4\" /><ac:link-body>S4-service</ac:link-body></ac:link></p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicio encargado de almacenar archivos (p&uacute;blicos y privados)</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-s4-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-s4-service</a> </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>selling-service</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>vPOS-service</p></td><td><ul><li><p>Servicios que permiten a un comercio que un usuario pague sus productos a trav&eacute;s de internet (Similar a Paypal)</p></li></ul></td><td><p><a href=\"https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-vpos-service\">https://github.com/bancardsa/bancard-vpos-service</a> </p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr /><p><em>Conoc&eacute; nuestros portales</em> &darr;</p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Portales de Bancard\" ri:version-at-save=\"6\" /><ac:link-body>Portales de Bancard</ac:link-body></ac:link><p> </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2794160273"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":190688538},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2794160273/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2794160273/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2794160273/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2794160273/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2794160273","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2794160273/Servicios+de+Bancard","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2794160273","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2794160273","tinyui":"/x/kYCLpg","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}